              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>The structure of this document comprises:</xhtml:p>
<xhtml:ul>
                      <xhtml:li>a general section that covers all assumptions and constraints that are always applicable, and</xhtml:li>
                      <xhtml:li>at least one section for each ASIL component that covers its constraints and necessary verification steps. The section for a component is identified by its module abbreviation.</xhtml:li>
                    </xhtml:ul>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
