              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>Vector's assumptions on the environment of the MICROSAR Safe components as well as the integration process are described.</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
