        <SPEC-OBJECT IDENTIFIER="id-1bf889e8d47a10b349ccb7fab858c802" LAST-CHANGE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00" LONG-NAME="76d6b38665cded08dfce721420803d5ab02b5a09bad5a429290506cdcc2e7cea">
          <VALUES>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="76d6b38665cded08dfce721420803d5ab02b5a09bad5a429290506cdcc2e7cea">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>id-474bf8df001703d4f13bcf6621ec60e3</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>id-356fa0b261512705956dc6124b01c001</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>
MICROSAR Safe must be configured using the DaVinci tools. MICROSAR Safe must be compiled by using a compiler for the target hardware.
<xhtml:br/>
These tools must be evaluated with respect to their impact on functional safety by the user.
</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="DocItem">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>id-83df1902a3d82b5ad802413febd9486c</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE THE-VALUE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>id-aa6269f32be4c61f516adebdbf3b1e19</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE THE-VALUE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>id-1deeefdd91604feff8470574ac6fef3d</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE>
          </VALUES>
          <TYPE>
            <SPEC-OBJECT-TYPE-REF>id-9005dd4fc53fa9c4b4bcb1b9bddbb116</SPEC-OBJECT-TYPE-REF>
          </TYPE>
        </SPEC-OBJECT>
        <SPEC-OBJECT IDENTIFIER="id-69c60ddb2528b26cddc9e87282dc276b" LAST-CHANGE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00" LONG-NAME="63ec5225c65315d3049b33f4483975e29b67bc524d7c17dd912b0f077331d69f">
          <VALUES>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="63ec5225c65315d3049b33f4483975e29b67bc524d7c17dd912b0f077331d69f">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>id-474bf8df001703d4f13bcf6621ec60e3</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>id-356fa0b261512705956dc6124b01c001</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>It is assumed that the user of MICROSAR Safe evaluates and qualifies the defined compiler (incl. options) and linker according to ISO 26262 Part 8 Clause 11.</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="DocItem">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>id-83df1902a3d82b5ad802413febd9486c</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE THE-VALUE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>id-aa6269f32be4c61f516adebdbf3b1e19</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE THE-VALUE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>id-1deeefdd91604feff8470574ac6fef3d</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE>
          </VALUES>
          <TYPE>
            <SPEC-OBJECT-TYPE-REF>id-9005dd4fc53fa9c4b4bcb1b9bddbb116</SPEC-OBJECT-TYPE-REF>
          </TYPE>
        </SPEC-OBJECT>
        <SPEC-OBJECT IDENTIFIER="id-ccdcb9fb13a814939bdde49d42e99d0d" LAST-CHANGE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00" LONG-NAME="a451a88864295f994976eb5138f982ff03510d712f0821a54ef0cf72817abb70">
          <VALUES>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="a451a88864295f994976eb5138f982ff03510d712f0821a54ef0cf72817abb70">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>id-474bf8df001703d4f13bcf6621ec60e3</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>id-356fa0b261512705956dc6124b01c001</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>
The DaVinci Developer and DaVinci Configurator are assumed to have an impact on functional safety. In the first place, only a tool error detection level of two can be expected.
<xhtml:br/>
The resulting tool confidence level (TCL) would require a qualification of those tools.
</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="DocItem">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>id-83df1902a3d82b5ad802413febd9486c</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE THE-VALUE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>id-aa6269f32be4c61f516adebdbf3b1e19</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE THE-VALUE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>id-1deeefdd91604feff8470574ac6fef3d</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE>
          </VALUES>
          <TYPE>
            <SPEC-OBJECT-TYPE-REF>id-9005dd4fc53fa9c4b4bcb1b9bddbb116</SPEC-OBJECT-TYPE-REF>
          </TYPE>
        </SPEC-OBJECT>
        <SPEC-OBJECT IDENTIFIER="id-9687220d307ed18bae645aca916095ce" LAST-CHANGE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00" LONG-NAME="62ccfb4fac4175e2e57d008481028e499970e8c86419a3c02a0a11acf8a5e1f7">
          <VALUES>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="62ccfb4fac4175e2e57d008481028e499970e8c86419a3c02a0a11acf8a5e1f7">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>id-474bf8df001703d4f13bcf6621ec60e3</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>id-356fa0b261512705956dc6124b01c001</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>To ensure freedom from interference with respect to memory for the BSW, Vector provides the MICROSAR Safe Silence Verifier (MSSV). </xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="DocItem">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>id-83df1902a3d82b5ad802413febd9486c</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE THE-VALUE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>id-aa6269f32be4c61f516adebdbf3b1e19</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE THE-VALUE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>id-1deeefdd91604feff8470574ac6fef3d</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE>
          </VALUES>
          <TYPE>
            <SPEC-OBJECT-TYPE-REF>id-9005dd4fc53fa9c4b4bcb1b9bddbb116</SPEC-OBJECT-TYPE-REF>
          </TYPE>
        </SPEC-OBJECT>
        <SPEC-OBJECT IDENTIFIER="id-74b640f2ea01cca10619e938202eda02" LAST-CHANGE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00" LONG-NAME="0ffd7da9903a36e0077871e40f950dff7e7b70356356ae3f290c6d82a2139535">
          <VALUES>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="0ffd7da9903a36e0077871e40f950dff7e7b70356356ae3f290c6d82a2139535">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>id-474bf8df001703d4f13bcf6621ec60e3</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>id-356fa0b261512705956dc6124b01c001</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>To ensure freedom from interference with respect to memory and to detect additional faults that may have been introduced by the DaVinci tools for the RTE, Vector provides the RTE Analyzer.</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="DocItem">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>id-83df1902a3d82b5ad802413febd9486c</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE THE-VALUE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>id-aa6269f32be4c61f516adebdbf3b1e19</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE THE-VALUE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>id-1deeefdd91604feff8470574ac6fef3d</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-DATE-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-DATE>
          </VALUES>
          <TYPE>
            <SPEC-OBJECT-TYPE-REF>id-9005dd4fc53fa9c4b4bcb1b9bddbb116</SPEC-OBJECT-TYPE-REF>
          </TYPE>
        </SPEC-OBJECT>
        <SPEC-OBJECT IDENTIFIER="id-15a63605511d1b07822f1d055ee85568" LAST-CHANGE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00" LONG-NAME="f6d4af2f987e61b48cd30cc339c10fe0ede52f1ad9810643514e57accaea451c">
          <VALUES>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="f6d4af2f987e61b48cd30cc339c10fe0ede52f1ad9810643514e57accaea451c">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>id-474bf8df001703d4f13bcf6621ec60e3</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>id-356fa0b261512705956dc6124b01c001</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>If MSSV and RTE Analyzer are used according to their Technical References and the Safety Manual, the tool confidence level for the DaVinci tools can be reduced to TCL1 by the user of MICROSAR Safe.</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
