        <SPEC-OBJECT IDENTIFIER="id-65f937c52ec7418c6144801941148168" LAST-CHANGE="2023-04-17T14:14:08.073-04:00" LONG-NAME="0bf75a192260f939c177225637f4b2e1552e5f7825f7e6d5c31165ee1a31c1be">
          <VALUES>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="0bf75a192260f939c177225637f4b2e1552e5f7825f7e6d5c31165ee1a31c1be">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>id-474bf8df001703d4f13bcf6621ec60e3</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>id-356fa0b261512705956dc6124b01c001</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>
<xhtml:strong>The user of MICROSAR Safe shall not use functionality of MICROSAR Safe components marked with a BETA-ESCAN.</xhtml:strong>
</xhtml:p>
<xhtml:p>
Functionality marked with a BETA-ESCAN is not thoroughly tested by Vector.
<xhtml:br/>
Vector ensures that functionality marked with a BETA-ESCAN can be completely disabled.
</xhtml:p>
<xhtml:p>The list of ESCANs (incl. BETA-ESCANs) is provided with a delivery. </xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
