              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>E2EXF requires the following functionality as safety requirements from the RTE:</xhtml:p>
<xhtml:ul>
                      <xhtml:li>Transformer handling (TSR-10)</xhtml:li>
                    </xhtml:ul>
<xhtml:p>For components provided as part of MICROSAR Safe, the respective section of the Safety Manual for that component allows you identifying if this requirement is fulfilled.</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
