              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>This component requires the OS service to get the core ID functionality as an assumed safety requirement (TSR-1) from other interfacing components.</xhtml:p>
<xhtml:p>For components provided as part of MICROSAR Safe, the respective section of the Safety Manual for that component allows you identifying if this requirement is fulfilled.</xhtml:p>
<xhtml:p>This requirement is only applicable if TSR-1 is assumed as a safety requirement.</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
