                          <xhtml:td>TSR-6</xhtml:td>
                          <xhtml:td>ASIL D</xhtml:td>
                        </xhtml:tr>
                        <xhtml:tr>
                          <xhtml:td>CREQ-130</xhtml:td>
                          <xhtml:td>OS shall allow to share stacks between tasks which do not preempt each other.</xhtml:td>
                          <xhtml:td>TSR-7</xhtml:td>
                          <xhtml:td>ASIL D</xhtml:td>
                        </xhtml:tr>
                        <xhtml:tr>
                          <xhtml:td>CREQ-115010</xhtml:td>
                          <xhtml:td>OS shall provide a callback for signalling a task activation.</xhtml:td>
                          <xhtml:td>TSR-6</xhtml:td>
                          <xhtml:td>ASIL D</xhtml:td>
                        </xhtml:tr>
                        <xhtml:tr>
                          <xhtml:td>CREQ-115028</xhtml:td>
                          <xhtml:td>OS shall provide a callback for signalling the setting of an event.</xhtml:td>
                          <xhtml:td>TSR-6</xhtml:td>
                          <xhtml:td>ASIL D</xhtml:td>
                        </xhtml:tr>
                        <xhtml:tr>
                          <xhtml:td>CREQ-115029</xhtml:td>
                          <xhtml:td>OS shall provide a callback for signalling a thread switch.</xhtml:td>
