<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>
The user of MICROSAR Safe shall verify that the API functions <xhtml:em>Os_EnableLevel[KM|UM|AM]</xhtml:em> are only called if interrupts were disabled previously by calling the corresponding <xhtml:em>Os_DisableLevel[KM|UM|AM]</xhtml:em> function.
