              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>
The user of MICROSAR Safe shall verify the generated value of the define <xhtml:em>OS_HAL_MP_STACK_REGION_NUMBER</xhtml:em> in <xhtml:em>Os_Hal_MemoryProtection_Cfg.h</xhtml:em>. The value must be a valid region number provided by the hardware.
</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
