              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>
The following hardware safety manual has been taken into consideration:
<xhtml:br/>
File Name: S32K14XSM.pdf
<xhtml:br/>
S32K14x Series Safety Manual
<xhtml:br/>
Doc. No. S32K14XSM
</xhtml:p>
<xhtml:p>
This OS does not implement any requirement from that safety manuals.
<xhtml:br/>
It is assumed that the requirements related to OS functionality are related to latent faults only and the aimed ASIL is still achievable without implementation by the OS.
</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
