            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>id-356fa0b261512705956dc6124b01c001</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>
<xhtml:strong>The user of MICROSAR Safe shall disable Logical Execution Time Support for ASIL software</xhtml:strong>
<xhtml:br/>
No Rte_LetFrame_&lt;frame>_Release and Rte_LetFrame_&lt;frame>_Terminate functions shall exist in the code.
<xhtml:br/>
The RTE Analyzer reports not supported template variants in case it detects usage of LET.
</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
