              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>id-356fa0b261512705956dc6124b01c001</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>
<xhtml:strong>The user of MICROSAR Safe shall disable ArrayImplPolicy PayloadAsPointerToArray for safety related SWCs</xhtml:strong>
<xhtml:br/>
The RTE Analyzer reports not supported template variants in case it detects usage of arrays with ArrayImplPolicy set to PayloadAsPointerToArray.
</xhtml:p>
