            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>id-356fa0b261512705956dc6124b01c001</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>
<xhtml:strong>The user of MICROSAR Safe shall execute the RTE Analyzer on Windows.</xhtml:strong>
<xhtml:br/>
MICROSAR Classic RTE Analyzer for Linux is not yet qualified for series production.
</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
