              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>id-356fa0b261512705956dc6124b01c001</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>The RTE requires the following functionality as safety requirements from the NVM:</xhtml:p>
<xhtml:ul>
                      <xhtml:li>Reading blocks (TSR-5)</xhtml:li>
                      <xhtml:li>Writing blocks (TSR-4)</xhtml:li>
                    </xhtml:ul>
<xhtml:p>
For components provided as part of MICROSAR Safe, the respective section of the Safety Manual for that component allows you identifying if this requirement is fulfilled.
<xhtml:br/>
This requirement only applies if TSR-4 and TSR-5 are considered a safety requirement.
</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
