              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>This component requires sending and receiving functionality as an assumed safety requirement (TSR-111108) from other interfacing components.</xhtml:p>
<xhtml:p>For components provided as part of MICROSAR Safe, the respective section of the Safety Manual for that component allows you identifying if this requirement is fulfilled.</xhtml:p>
<xhtml:p>This requirement is only applicable if TSR-111108 is assumed as a safety requirement.</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
