              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>
The user of MICROSAR Safe shall verify that the output path of the generator is empty before the generator is started.
<xhtml:br/>
The output path can be defined by the command line argument <xhtml:em>OUTPUT-DIRECTORY</xhtml:em>.
</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
