              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>
The user of MICROSAR Safe shall use the WdgM only on 32-bit microcontroller platforms.
<xhtml:br/>
This requirement is necessary to ensure usage in a released configuration.
</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
