              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>id-356fa0b261512705956dc6124b01c001</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-XHTML-REF>
              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>
The user of MICROSAR Safe shall verify that for each core with ID <xhtml:em>WDGM_NR_OF_WATCHDOGS_CORE&lt;ID></xhtml:em> matches the actual number of configured WD devices.
<xhtml:br/>
The define can be found in <xhtml:em>WdgM_Cfg.h</xhtml:em>.
</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
