              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>This component requires setting a trigger condition and setting the triggering mode as an assumed safety requirement (TSR-13, TSR-14, TSR-15) from WdgIf component.</xhtml:p>
<xhtml:p>For components provided as part of MICROSAR Safe, the respective section of the Safety Manual for that component allows you identifying if this requirement is fulfilled.</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
              </THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
