              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE>
                <xhtml:div>
<xhtml:div>
<xhtml:p>
The user of MICROSAR Safe shall call the service to set the mode as expected by the Wdg stack.
<xhtml:br/>
If the watchdog is not properly set up, it may not provide the expected protection.
</xhtml:p>
</xhtml:div>
</xhtml:div>
